NewVoiceMedia 'Interview Problem' code.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Written for Python 2.7.9

gameplayer.py            :- the initial source code written as a Python module
test/test_gameplayer.py  :- unit tests

GamePlayer.py            :- source code implemented as a Class
test/test_GamePlayer.py  :- unit tests

Tests run under pytest 3.2.3 (if pytest is not installed please run 'pip install -U pytest' first) :
$ python -m pytest -v

